headline: Baird Mid Cap Growth Equity Fund Q1 2025 Commentary
summary: For the quarter, the Baird Mid Cap Growth portfolio produced a negative return of -9.6%, net of fees, trailing the Russell Midcap Growth decline of -7.1%.
